description: PLEASE READ BEFORE YOU CALL OR COME IN!!!     Here is the skinny on this car:    Good to Go:    Take a Look at:    Link to Video:    **We rely 100% on our customers to inspect and be certain about the vehicle they are buying**     **Our ''product'' we stand behind is our ability to SELL CHEAP. Above are our notes on this vehicle. We are not mechanics so we rely on our customers opinion. Feel free to bring one  directional code readers, tools, or friends to help**    THIS IS WHO WE ARE AND WHAT WE DO-  My wife and I run a small used car dealership in Fort Madison, IA. We have found the greatest need is in cheap, affordable transportation. We try to sell our vehicles as cheap as we can. Our business model is simple...Sell more cars for less, and we know prices sell. So, due to our wholesale pricing we can not hold vehicles nor accept any payment other than cash. Our biggest goal is ''To put people in a better place''. We will be honest, and upfront with you. We will not hound you on the lot if you're just here to look, nor will we play games with our prices. We are a no-haggle dealer and put a lot of pride in being BLUNT and UPFRONT. We don't offer any financing as we truly believe in the long run that won't help a short term problem. Be honest with us and we will do our best to help you find your next vehicle--even if that's not buying one from us.   Call/Text 309-337-1049 or 309-267-7200 or visit our site for quickest info www.highlifeauto.com
